<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">1.合奏《赶花会》                                           刘明源曲</span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">      《古城新貌》                                     　　刘明源曲</span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: #000000; font-size: small;">　        　　三弦领奏：张馨元</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">2.女声独唱《一杯美酒》                                    艾克拜尔曲</span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: #000000; font-size: small;">　　        　演唱：唐文娟</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">3.笛子独奏《姑苏行》                                        江先渭曲</span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">             笛子演奏：马芸（文华奖获奖者）</span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">4.丝弦五重奏《欢乐的夜晚》                                   胡登跳曲</span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">            《天山之春》               乌斯满江、俞礼纯曲  王范地改编</span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">             演奏：尹秋薇、肖珺华、王雅雯、靳雨薇、傅琼 </span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">5.京胡与乐队《柳青娘》                                         吴华曲</span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">             京胡演奏：张学琴    司鼓：李文博</span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">6.古筝独奏《春到湘江》                            宁保生曲  王中山改编</span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">             古筝演奏：王雅雯</span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">7.男声独唱《山歌唱出好兆头》                          郑南词  饶荣发曲</span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: #000000; font-size: small;">　       　  演唱：尤龙</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">8.琵琶独奏《春雨》                                       朱毅、文博曲</span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: #000000; font-size: small;">　　         琵琶演奏：蒋彦（CCTV光荣绽放十大青年琵琶演奏家）</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">9.合奏《洗衣歌》                                  西藏民歌  刘明源编曲</span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">      《节日的欢乐》                                         刘明源曲</span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">              新疆木碗唢呐领奏：陈力宝  </span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">10.男女声二重唱《想亲亲》                                     山西民歌</span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; color: #000000; font-size: small;">　　          演唱：唐文娟、尤龙 </span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">11.板胡独奏《四季套曲——春》                                 刘明源曲</span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">           《云雀》                       罗马尼亚民间乐曲  刘明源改编</span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">              演奏：刘湘（国家一级演员）</span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">12.合奏《花好月圆》                               黄贻钧曲  彭修文改编</span></span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">       《新编喜洋洋——幸福年》                      刘明源曲  刘湘改编<br /></span></span></p>
